----
This holiday, which commemorates some ancient blood rite or other, involves people dressing in weird clothes and going door-to-door threatening to commit acts of petty vandalism unless the homeowner gives you candy. It's good fun for all involved, except the half-orc hoboes, who complain that when they do exactly the same thing, they get arrested.

==Details==
[[Halloween]] is that time of year when Adventurers dress up and scam candy off total strangers. Or something. It occurs each [[Kingdom of Loathing Calendar|Porktober 8]]. To go trick-or-treating, you need an [[:Category:Outfits|outfit]]. Each round of trick-or-treating costs an Adventure, and is available from the main map.

